headline.main: U.S. Soccer Introduces a Rule That National Team Players Must Stand for the Anthem
headline.print_headline: U.S. Soccer Introduces a Rule That National Team Players Must Stand for the Anthem

lead_paragraph: Lizzy Wendell scored 25 points, leading three Bulldogs to reach 20, and No. 22 Drake beat Wichita State 105-89 on Saturday, winning its 19th straight game and becoming the first team to go undefeated in Missouri Valley Conference regular-season play.
